params.sqlcmd: "select " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"LOAD_PLAN_CD\\" as \\"LOAD_PLAN_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" to_char(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", 'yyyy/mm/dd') as \\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", " +" to_char(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ODR_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ODR_QTY\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"LOAD_PLAN_COMMENT\\" as \\"LOAD_PLAN_COMMENT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_LOAD_PLAN " +"where " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" = ? " +" and T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ? " +" and TO_CHAR(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", 'yyyy/mm/dd') >= ? " +" and TO_CHAR(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", 'yyyy/mm/dd') <= ? " +" and T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PLANT_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ITEM_CD\\""
"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ODR_LT\\" + M_ITEM.\\"FIXED_LT\\" + M_ITEM.\\"SAFETY_LT\\" + M_ITEM.\\"ISSUE_LT\\" as \\"ITEM_LT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"
"select " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM " +"where " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = ?"

"select " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"PROGRAM_CD\\" as \\"PROGRAM_CD\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FUNCTION_NAME\\" as \\"FUNCTION_NAME\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"BUSINESS_GROUP_CD\\" as \\"BUSINESS_GROUP_CD\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"BUSINESS_CD\\" as \\"BUSINESS_CD\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FILE_PATH\\" as \\"FILE_PATH\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FILE_NAME\\" as \\"FILE_NAME\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"LOG_MODE_TYP\\" as \\"LOG_MODE_TYP\\", " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"OUTPUT_MODE_TYP\\" as \\"OUTPUT_MODE_TYP\\" " +"from " +" SYS_BAT_PARM " +"where " +" SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"PROGRAM_CD\\" = ? " +" and SYS_BAT_PARM.\\"FUNCTION_NAME\\" = ?"

"select " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"LOAD_PLAN_CD\\" as \\"LOAD_PLAN_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PLANT_CD\\" as \\"PLANT_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"JOB_ODR_CD\\" as \\"JOB_ODR_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ITEM_CD\\" as \\"ITEM_CD\\", " +" M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_NAME\\" as \\"ITEM_NAME\\", " +" to_char(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", 'yyyy/mm/dd') as \\"PRD_DUE_DATE\\", " +" to_char(T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ODR_QTY\\", 'fm999999999999999990.0999') as \\"ODR_QTY\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"MODIFY_COUNT\\" as \\"MODIFY_COUNT\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"CUST_CD\\" as \\"CUST_CD\\", " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"LOAD_PLAN_COMMENT\\" as \\"LOAD_PLAN_COMMENT\\" " +"from " +" M_ITEM, " +" T_LOAD_PLAN " +"where " +" T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"LOAD_PLAN_CD\\" = ? " +" and M_ITEM.\\"ITEM_CD\\" = T_LOAD_PLAN.\\"ITEM_CD\\""
